  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "The promised land for climbers in the fives. Around 40 routes, including loads of excellent easier lines. A good place to practise trad climbing. Easily accessible and child-friendly. The crag goes into shade towards evening, while cooling trees make it pleasant even during the day. Abseil anchors are located above Start och Speed and Vårtecknet. Do not park on Ungmästaregatan.",
        "method": "llm",
        "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
        "sourceIds": [
          "legacy:gardsas"
        ]
      },
      "sections": {
        "allmant": {
          "title": {
            "text": "General",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "The promised land for grade 5 climbers. Around 40 routes, including lots of good easier lines. A great place to practise trad climbing. Easily accessible and child-friendly. The crag falls into shade towards evening, while the cooling trees make it pleasant even during the day. Abseil anchors are located above Start och Speed and Vårtecknet. Do not park on Ungmästaregatan.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          }
        },
        "introduktion": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Introduction",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Keep noise levels down, as the climbing is right next to residential properties; see Access below. Do not park on Ungmästaregatan!\n\nFor the descent, either head right to the cycle path or follow a steep path down to the left of Älgens överaskning.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          }
        },
        "karaktar": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Character",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Varied climbing, including large roofs. Mostly vertical, with a few ramps offering easy-angled climbing for beginners. Trad. Two glue-in bolt anchors, mainly for abseiling, fitted with a ring and maillon rapide; abseil from the ring and use your own carabiners for top-roping. Do not place any new bolts at Gärdsås—the crag is great as it is without bolts!",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          }
        },
        "vagbeskrivning": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Directions",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Park along Gärdsåsgatan or Kamgatan. Do NOT park by the recycling station on Ungmästaregatan, as previously stated here. Walk uphill and turn left onto Sockerbagaregatan. The street becomes a cycle path, and the crag then comes into view.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          }
        },
        "access": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Access",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "The climbing is very close to residential gardens. On the left-hand side of the area, you are literally climbing directly above some poor soul trying to read the paper in peace on their lawn. Do not shout unnecessarily, and avoid swearing or other bad behaviour. Please also park considerately. Do not park on Ungmästaregatan.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          }
        },
        "jannes-horn": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Jannes hörn",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Keep noise levels down on all routes up to Jennys grej, as the houses are very close by!",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:gardsas"
            ]
          }
        },
        "bikupan": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Bikupan",
            "method": "llm",
